<hr>
<h5>PHASE 2</h5>
<p>
Move GNFD (material salvage) from 14621 WESTBROOK to proposed location with shipping containers as sound barriers and storage. Complete TARO swales and continue building compost lanes.
</p>
<p>Finger farms running east to west start with a shipping container angled slightly toward sunset. These modular plots allow tennants to tweak "blue/green" models while giving the city time to evaluate project scaleability.</p>
<p>Each farm will have at least one shipping container placed as far east as possible to allow larger southern facing gardens. Rainwater will be harvested however drinking water would be supplied  by FOURSIGHT FARM until proper filtration systems are reliable. Electricity will be produced through solar panels and windmills. 
</p>
